model.name: Homepolish
model.bio:
__What’s your favorite Teen Vogue moment?__ Well, we're a bit biased but we really like the fashion intern desk story we did with you!  
 
__What beauty product are you loving right now?__ Everyone in the office has been really into face mists lately! They're a nice late afternoon pick-me-up.  
 
__What’s your go-to karaoke song?__ We listen to a LOT of Beyonce in the office. We named our meeting rooms after three of her songs.  

__What’s a goal you have for the rest of this year?__ Transform as many lives with interior design as possible!   

__If you had to describe yourself in a GIF, what would it be?__ [This one](http://i.giphy.com/fPKavkCyl9vOw.gif).    

*Visit [homepolish.com](http://www.homepolish.com) for more beautiful, affordable interior design by the hour.*
